\begin{itemize}
\item $x_i\in\mathcal{X}$: task
\item $y_i^\star$: true label (unobserved)
\item $y_i^{(j)}\in[K]$: label observed
\item $\pi^{(j)}\in\mathbb{R}^{K\times K}$: confusion matrix
\item $\pi^{g}\in\mathbb{R}^{K\times K}$: global confusion matrix
\item $s_i^{(j)}\in\{0,1\}$: confusion source
\end{itemize}
